summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed, including:  
  - Ratification of Tranche 1 Placement shares (81.49% approval).  
  - Approval for Tranche 2 Placement shares (89.27% approval).  
  - Related-party placements to directors (92.9–93.03% approval).  
  - Capital consolidation (93.42% approval).  

**Key Takeaway**: Shareholders endorsed capital raising (Placement) and capital restructuring, confirming investor support for equity issuances and consolidation. No material new financial/operational data disclosed.
